        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
            <span class="inline-block text-brandGold text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Portfolio</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif mb-6">Our Projects</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">Explore our curated collection of architectural achievements, showcasing our commitment to design, functionality, and sustainability.</p>
        </div>
